edu.calpoly.twitter

Class JSONTwitterGatherer

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.calpoly.twitter.JSONTwitterGatherer

  • public class JSONTwitterGatherer
extends Object
    Get tweets from Twitter. After getting tweets, it will put them in the specified store. After constructed, just call update() when you want it to fetch tweets.
